        " اَلصَّادِقُ عَلَيْهِ اَلسَّلاَمُ : «لاَ تَدْخُلُوا مَنَازِلَكُمْ بِمَكَّةَ إِذَا زُرْتُمْ يَعْنِي أَهْلَ مَكَّةَ »."
      ],
      "translations": {
        "en.bab-ul-qaim-publications": [
          "Hadith.3011 - Imam Jafar ibn Muhammad Al-Sadiq (as) said:\n\"Do not enter your homes in Mecca when you have visited, meaning the residents of Mecca.\""
        ]
